description-en: Homemade soup with chicken fillet, noodles, and vegetables, complemented by a boiled egg and fresh dill.

description-en: Rich borscht with veal, potatoes, cabbage, and beets, served with sour cream.

description-en: Rich broth with veal, Korean noodles, mushrooms, and spinach, complemented by sesame and pickled ginger.

description-en: Aromatic Uzbek soup with juicy dumplings, meat broth, and fresh herbs.

description-en: Hearty mastava with veal, rice, vegetables, and aromatic spices.

description-en: Rich broth with tender lamb, vegetables, and aromatic spices, complemented by fresh herbs.

description-ru: Пряный тайский суп на кокосовом молоке с креветками, грибами, черри и ароматной кинзой.

description-en: Spicy Thai soup with coconut milk, shrimp, mushrooms, cherry tomatoes, and fragrant cilantro.

description-en: Aromatic dish with veal, starch noodles, mushrooms, and tomatoes, complemented by semi-bitter pepper and a tangy sauce.

description-ru: Пряный азиатский бульон с тигровыми креветками, корейской лапшой, грибами и шпинатом, дополненный кунжутом и маринованным имбирем.
